## Import


An existing resource can be imported using its type token, name, and identifier, e.g.

```sh
$ pulumi import azure-native:azuredata:SqlServerInstance testsqlServerInstance /subscriptions/00000000-1111-2222-3333-444444444444/resourceGroups/testrg/providers/Microsoft.AzureData/SqlServerInstances/testsqlServerInstance 
```
